  Scenario: when defining a rule to generate new entities from existing relations, an error is thrown
    Given typeql define
      """
      define

      baseEntity sub entity,
          plays baseRelation:role1,
          plays baseRelation:role2;

      derivedEntity sub entity,
          plays baseRelation:role1,
          plays baseRelation:role2;

